使用YTPlayer 套件



1.複製video資料夾 (裡面必須包含 jquery.mb.YTPlayer.js   jquery.mb.YTPlayer.min.css  jquery.mb.YTPlayer.min.js 這三個檔案 )


2.
    複製以下放到<head>
    
    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.4.min.js"></script>
    <script src="video/jquery.mb.YTPlayer.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="video/jquery.mb.YTPlayer.min.css" />


3.於<body>中增加以下div

  <div id="bgVideo" data-property="{
  videoURL: 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tq75nkjL6a8', (可更改為想放置的url)
  mute: true,
  showControls: false
}">影片檔案</div>



4. 於jquery上增加語法

  $(document).ready(function(){
  $("#bgVideo").YTPlayer();
});


5. CDN(使用3.1.2版本)
    <script src="video/jquery.mb.YTPlayer.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery.mb.YTPlayer/3.1.2/jquery.mb.YTPlayer.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery.mb.YTPlayer/3.1.2/css/jquery.mb.YTPlayer.min.css" />




查看更多資訊連上此 https://tech.jastin.net/jquery-mb-ytplayer/
     
                https://cdnjs.com/libraries/jquery.mb.YTPlayer